### 1. Python Cache Files (Auto-generated)
```
DELETE ALL:
__pycache__/ (21 directories)
*.pyc files (81 files)
```

**Why**: These are automatically generated by Python and will be recreated when needed.

**How to delete**:
```powershell
# PowerShell (run from project root)
Get-ChildItem -Path . -Recurse -Filter "__pycache__" -Directory | Remove-Item -Recurse -Force
Get-ChildItem -Path . -Recurse -Filter "*.pyc" -File | Remove-Item -Force
```
